result.name: Paisano's Pizzeria Discovery Bay

reviews.text: Great service!! Cheap and tasty pizza. Can't go wrong here!

Good value for money, this is a go-to for birthday celebrations, school shared lunches, quick and easy group lunches or dinners.  The menu is simple...mainly pizza. Last time we were there it was so cold outside at the end of the Team Fear race. The place was packed with people wanting to eat in and take away.  The orders can take up to 45 minutes for a full pizza during their exceptionally busy times.  Recommend.
Good pizza, good food, good overall
Food is well priced, variety of pizza and other Italian dishes. Small seating area or takeaway.

One of the only places you can get good pizza in HK. However apart from its pizza, the other options are a bit of a disappointment and definitely not worth the value for money. Staff attitude was a bit passive, but you do really come here for its pizza which were prepared quick enough!
